4 bill having a fiscal impact, which amendment does not change any
5 factor of an actuarial investigation specified in subsection A of
6 Section 3109 of this title;
7 5. "Nonfiscal retirement bill" means a retirement bill:
8 a. which does not affect the cost or funding factors of a
9 retirement system,
10 b. which affects such factors only in a manner which does
